{"tid":745163,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"終於到我部LG G4 脫銲...","createTime":"2018-07-16T13:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T06:58:21.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c885b84761b9458e9b4a9fd88665a5f4109e74eb","tid":745163,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T13:49:04.000Z","msg":"開唔到機，長期hold住LG開機畫面，<br />\n試過跟台仔用風筒直接吹手機背面上少少嗰個位，<br />\n吹吹下右上角閃咗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n跟住開過幾次機情況依舊，<br />\n擺咗成日再開一次機，<br />\n開到但係check到粒u成8X度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n再用多陣又自動同我自動reboot，<br />\n又hold死咗喺LG開機畫面到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n唔想益手機舖(當你燒底板，要五舊水至肯整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，<br />\n打算自己學鬼佬拆塊底板出嚟再用風筒吹吹粒U，<br />\n想問有咩嘢要注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋有少少問題：<br />\n1. 隻螺絲批邊度買到？<br />\n2. 係咪可以自己搽散熱膏幫助散熱？"},{"pid":"5438ad6b3effed01ed9e101b007548023b4d2516","tid":745163,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"Me too<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ec74ea1581e185d80b2127aa4ff06c47c0870a","tid":745163,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5438ad6b3effed01ed9e101b007548023b4d2516","tid":745163,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"Me too<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:02:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nzS74breY4A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnzS74breY4A&d=qqEyEHjbM5O92X0SLE5yGhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=6f6c0d54\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?